PhysicalTable.name: SAMP_ADDRESSES_D
PhysicalTable.Description: Addresses Dimension table: Stores address attribute information. This information is mainly used for plotting maps within OBIEE visualization.

PhysicalColumn.name: Iso_Country_code3
PhysicalColumn.Description: ISO Country Code: Stores the ISO country code as a text

PhysicalColumn.name: Estab_Name
PhysicalColumn.Description: Establishment Name: Stores the establishment name as a text

PhysicalColumn.name: Region
PhysicalColumn.Description: Region: Stores the region information as a text

PhysicalColumn.name: Ctry_Cd3_State_Abbrv
PhysicalColumn.Description: Country Code State Abbrevation: Stores the country code concatenated with the state abbrevation

PhysicalColumn.name: Ctry_Cd3_State_Name
PhysicalColumn.Description: Country Code State Name: Stores the country code concatenated with state name

PhysicalColumn.name: Ctry_Cd3_State_Name_City
PhysicalColumn.Description: Country Code State Name City: Stores the country code concatenated with state name concatenated with city name

PhysicalColumn.name: State_Province_Abbrv
PhysicalColumn.Description: State Province Abbrevation: Stores the state province abbrevation as a text

PhysicalColumn.name: State_Province
PhysicalColumn.Description: State Provice: Stores the state province name as a text

PhysicalColumn.name: Address_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Address Key: Surrogate key of the address dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Address1
PhysicalColumn.Description: Address1: Stores address1 as a text

PhysicalColumn.name: Area
PhysicalColumn.Description: Area: Stores area information as a text

PhysicalColumn.name: Address2
PhysicalColumn.Description: Address2: Stores address2 as a text

PhysicalColumn.name: City
PhysicalColumn.Description: City: Stores city information as a text

PhysicalColumn.name: Postal_Code
PhysicalColumn.Description: Postal Code: Stores the postal code information as a double

PhysicalColumn.name: Country_Name
PhysicalColumn.Description: Country Name: Stores country name as a text

PhysicalColumn.name: Latitude
PhysicalColumn.Description: Latitude: Stores the latitude information as a double

PhysicalColumn.name: Longitude
PhysicalColumn.Description: Longitude: Stores the longitude information as a double
